data.eml:eml: Tanaidacea (Crustacea: Peracarida) from the Southern French Polynesia Expedition, 2014. I. Tanaidomorpha

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bird, Graham J. (2019): Tanaidacea (Crustacea: Peracarida) from the Southern French Polynesia Expedition, 2014. I. Tanaidomorpha. Zootaxa 4548 (1): 1-75, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4548.1.1
